{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":2097,"text":"The murder happened a little over 21 years ago,"},{"time":6569,"text":"January the 18th, 1991,"},{"time":10848,"text":"in a small"},{"time":13109,"text":"bedroom community"},{"time":15483,"text":"of Lynwood, California, just a few miles"},{"time":18318,"text":"southeast of Los Angeles."},{"time":20816,"text":"A father came out of his house"},{"time":23651,"text":"to tell his teenage son and his five friends"},{"time":27058,"text":"that it was time for them to stop horsing around"},{"time":29837,"text":"on the front lawn and on the sidewalk,"},{"time":32747,"text":"to get home, finish their schoolwork,"},{"time":35655,"text":"and prepare themselves for bed."},{"time":38401,"text":"And as the father was administering these instructions,"},{"time":41971,"text":"a car drove by, slowly,"},{"time":45309,"text":"and just after it passed the father and the teenagers,"},{"time":48211,"text":"a hand went out from the front passenger window,"},{"time":52199,"text":"and -- \"Bam, Bam!\" -- killing the father."},{"time":57461,"text":"And the car sped off."}]},{"cues":[{"time":60620,"text":"The police,"},{"time":62461,"text":"investigating officers, were amazingly efficient."},{"time":66291,"text":"They considered all the usual culprits,"},{"time":68721,"text":"and in less than 24 hours, they had selected their suspect:"},{"time":73288,"text":"Francisco Carrillo, a 17-year-old kid"},{"time":76866,"text":"who lived about two or three blocks away"},{"time":78903,"text":"from where the shooting occurred."},{"time":81638,"text":"They found photos of him. They prepared a photo array,"},{"time":86286,"text":"and the day after the shooting,"},{"time":89870,"text":"they showed it to one of the teenagers, and he said,"},{"time":92763,"text":"\"That's the picture."},{"time":95082,"text":"That's the shooter I saw that killed the father.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":100469,"text":"That was all a preliminary hearing judge had"},{"time":103046,"text":"to listen to, to bind Mr. Carrillo over to stand trial"},{"time":108155,"text":"for a first-degree murder."},{"time":110842,"text":"In the investigation that followed before the actual trial,"},{"time":114049,"text":"each of the other five teenagers was shown"},{"time":117460,"text":"photographs, the same photo array."},{"time":121508,"text":"The picture that we best can determine was probably"},{"time":124332,"text":"the one that they were shown in the photo array"},{"time":126604,"text":"is in your bottom left hand corner of these mug shots."},{"time":130301,"text":"The reason we're not sure absolutely is because"},{"time":133737,"text":"of the nature of evidence preservation"},{"time":138170,"text":"in our judicial system,"},{"time":140454,"text":"but that's another whole TEDx talk for later. (Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":145202,"text":"So at the actual trial,"},{"time":148108,"text":"all six of the teenagers testified,"},{"time":151108,"text":"and indicated the identifications they had made"},{"time":154866,"text":"in the photo array."},{"time":158342,"text":"He was convicted. He was sentenced to life imprisonment,"},{"time":163123,"text":"and transported to Folsom Prison."}]},{"cues":[{"time":168582,"text":"So what's wrong?"},{"time":170671,"text":"Straightforward, fair trial, full investigation."},{"time":175437,"text":"Oh yes, no gun was ever found."},{"time":178978,"text":"No vehicle was ever identified as being the one"},{"time":183132,"text":"in which the shooter had extended his arm,"},{"time":186356,"text":"and no person was ever charged with being the driver"},{"time":189641,"text":"of the shooter's vehicle."},{"time":192883,"text":"And Mr. Carrillo's alibi?"},{"time":196764,"text":"Which of those parents here in the room might not lie"},{"time":202058,"text":"concerning the whereabouts of your son or daughter"},{"time":204877,"text":"in an investigation of a killing?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":210874,"text":"Sent to prison,"},{"time":213596,"text":"adamantly insisting on his innocence,"},{"time":217094,"text":"which he has consistently for 21 years."}]},{"cues":[{"time":221831,"text":"So what's the problem?"},{"time":225302,"text":"The problems, actually, for this kind of case"},{"time":228026,"text":"come manyfold from decades of scientific research"},{"time":231935,"text":"involving human memory."},{"time":235837,"text":"First of all, we have all the statistical analyses"},{"time":238651,"text":"from the Innocence Project work,"},{"time":240858,"text":"where we know that we have, what,"},{"time":243555,"text":"250, 280 documented cases now where people have"},{"time":247336,"text":"been wrongfully convicted and subsequently exonerated,"},{"time":251408,"text":"some from death row, on the basis of later DNA analysis,"},{"time":257754,"text":"and you know that over three quarters of all of those cases"},{"time":261415,"text":"of exoneration involved only eyewitness identification"},{"time":267686,"text":"testimony during the trial that convicted them."},{"time":271333,"text":"We know that eyewitness identifications are fallible."}]},{"cues":[{"time":276508,"text":"The other comes from an interesting aspect"},{"time":278728,"text":"of human memory that's related to various brain functions"},{"time":281931,"text":"but I can sum up for the sake of brevity here"},{"time":284497,"text":"in a simple line:"},{"time":286881,"text":"The brain abhors a vacuum."},{"time":291629,"text":"Under the best of observation conditions,"},{"time":295539,"text":"the absolute best,"},{"time":297411,"text":"we only detect, encode and store in our brains"},{"time":301124,"text":"bits and pieces of the entire experience in front of us,"},{"time":304819,"text":"and they're stored in different parts of the brain."},{"time":307148,"text":"So now, when it's important for us to be able to recall"},{"time":311303,"text":"what it was that we experienced,"},{"time":314324,"text":"we have an incomplete, we have a partial store,"},{"time":319602,"text":"and what happens?"},{"time":322055,"text":"Below awareness, with no requirement for any kind of"},{"time":324879,"text":"motivated processing, the brain fills in information"},{"time":330050,"text":"that was not there,"},{"time":332475,"text":"not originally stored,"},{"time":334925,"text":"from inference, from speculation,"},{"time":337469,"text":"from sources of information that came to you,"},{"time":340281,"text":"as the observer, after the observation."},{"time":343416,"text":"But it happens without awareness such that"},{"time":345490,"text":"you don't, aren't even cognizant of it occurring."},{"time":349124,"text":"It's called reconstructed memories."},{"time":351391,"text":"It happens to us in all the aspects of our life, all the time."},{"time":355690,"text":"It was those two considerations, among others --"},{"time":358954,"text":"reconstructed memory, the fact about the eyewitness fallibility --"},{"time":363459,"text":"that was part of the instigation"},{"time":366515,"text":"for a group of appeal attorneys"},{"time":368964,"text":"led by an amazing lawyer named Ellen Eggers"},{"time":372436,"text":"to pool their experience and their talents together"},{"time":376564,"text":"and petition a superior court"},{"time":378401,"text":"for a retrial for Francisco Carrillo."},{"time":383471,"text":"They retained me, as a forensic neurophysiologist,"},{"time":387859,"text":"because I had expertise"},{"time":390001,"text":"in eyewitness memory identification,"},{"time":392121,"text":"which obviously makes sense for this case, right?"},{"time":395316,"text":"But also because I have expertise and testify about"},{"time":398660,"text":"the nature of human night vision."}]},{"cues":[{"time":403037,"text":"Well, what's that got to do with this?"},{"time":406070,"text":"Well, when you read through the case materials"},{"time":409372,"text":"in this Carrillo case,"},{"time":412094,"text":"one of the things that suddenly strikes you is that"},{"time":414924,"text":"the investigating officers said the lighting was good"},{"time":418414,"text":"at the crime scene, at the shooting."},{"time":421948,"text":"All the teenagers testified during the trial"},{"time":425405,"text":"that they could see very well."},{"time":428884,"text":"But this occurred in mid-January,"},{"time":431724,"text":"in the Northern Hemisphere, at 7 p.m. at night."},{"time":437723,"text":"So when I did the calculations"},{"time":440748,"text":"for the lunar data and the solar data"},{"time":442960,"text":"at that location on Earth at the time of the incident"},{"time":446139,"text":"of the shooting, all right,"},{"time":448187,"text":"it was well past the end of civil twilight"},{"time":450804,"text":"and there was no moon up that night."},{"time":453060,"text":"So all the light in this area from the sun and the moon"},{"time":455339,"text":"is what you see on the screen right here."},{"time":457923,"text":"The only lighting in that area had to come"},{"time":460837,"text":"from artificial sources,"},{"time":464107,"text":"and that's where I go out and I do the actual reconstruction"},{"time":466875,"text":"of the scene with photometers, with various measures"},{"time":469672,"text":"of illumination and various other measures of"},{"time":471646,"text":"color perception, along with special cameras"},{"time":476113,"text":"and high-speed film, right?"},{"time":478242,"text":"Take all the measurements and record them, right?"},{"time":481171,"text":"And then take photographs, and this is what the scene"},{"time":483328,"text":"looked like at the time of the shooting"},{"time":484763,"text":"from the position of the teenagers"},{"time":487229,"text":"looking at the car going by and shooting."},{"time":491051,"text":"This is looking directly across the street"},{"time":493356,"text":"from where they were standing."},{"time":495684,"text":"Remember, the investigating officers' report said"},{"time":498037,"text":"the lighting was good."},{"time":500270,"text":"The teenagers said they could see very well."},{"time":502704,"text":"This is looking down to the east,"},{"time":505955,"text":"where the shooting vehicle sped off,"},{"time":509651,"text":"and this is the lighting directly behind the father"},{"time":514543,"text":"and the teenagers."},{"time":516884,"text":"As you can see, it is at best poor."},{"time":520795,"text":"No one's going to call this well-lit, good lighting,"},{"time":524668,"text":"and in fact, as nice as these pictures are,"},{"time":527862,"text":"and the reason we take them is I knew I was going to have to testify in court,"},{"time":531323,"text":"and a picture is worth more than a thousand words"},{"time":534515,"text":"when you're trying to communicate numbers,"},{"time":536915,"text":"abstract concepts like lux, the international measurement"},{"time":540187,"text":"of illumination, the Ishihara color perception test values."},{"time":545363,"text":"When you present those to people who are not well-versed"},{"time":548524,"text":"in those aspects of science and that, they become"},{"time":551640,"text":"salamanders in the noonday sun. It's like"},{"time":554019,"text":"talking about the tangent of the visual angle, all right?"},{"time":556933,"text":"Their eyes just glaze over, all right?"},{"time":559718,"text":"A good forensic expert also has to be a good educator,"},{"time":564077,"text":"a good communicator, and that's part of the reason"},{"time":566236,"text":"why we take the pictures, to show not only"},{"time":568531,"text":"where the light sources are, and what we call the spill,"},{"time":571331,"text":"the distribution, but also so that it's easier"},{"time":573960,"text":"for the trier of fact to understand the circumstances."},{"time":577995,"text":"So these are some of the pictures that, in fact,"},{"time":580868,"text":"I used when I testified,"},{"time":583283,"text":"but more importantly were, to me as a scientist,"},{"time":585148,"text":"are those readings, the photometer readings,"},{"time":587131,"text":"which I can then convert into actual predictions"},{"time":591731,"text":"of the visual capability of the human eye"},{"time":595251,"text":"under those circumstances,"},{"time":597627,"text":"and from my readings that I recorded at the scene"},{"time":601275,"text":"under the same solar and lunar conditions"},{"time":603515,"text":"at the same time, so on and so forth, right,"},{"time":606507,"text":"I could predict"},{"time":607913,"text":"that there would be no reliable color perception,"},{"time":610105,"text":"which is crucial for face recognition,"},{"time":612419,"text":"and that there would be only scotopic vision,"},{"time":614731,"text":"which means there would be very little resolution,"},{"time":616691,"text":"what we call boundary or edge detection,"},{"time":618939,"text":"and that furthermore, because the eyes would have been"},{"time":621254,"text":"totally dilated under this light, the depth of field,"},{"time":625059,"text":"the distance at which you can focus and see details,"},{"time":628217,"text":"would have been less than 18 inches away."}]},{"cues":[{"time":633611,"text":"I testified to that to the court,"},{"time":636115,"text":"and while the judge was very attentive,"},{"time":638548,"text":"it had been a very, very long hearing"},{"time":641155,"text":"for this petition for a retrial, and as a result,"},{"time":645899,"text":"I noticed out of the corner of my eye"},{"time":647659,"text":"that I thought that maybe the judge was going to need"},{"time":651804,"text":"a little more of a nudge"},{"time":653867,"text":"than just more numbers."}]},{"cues":[{"time":656375,"text":"And here I became a bit audacious,"},{"time":658667,"text":"and I turned"},{"time":660187,"text":"and I asked the judge,"},{"time":662579,"text":"I said, \"Your Honor, I think you should go out"},{"time":664987,"text":"and look at the scene yourself.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":667691,"text":"Now I may have used a tone which was more like a dare"},{"time":670832,"text":"than a request — (Laughter) —"},{"time":673236,"text":"but nonetheless, it's to this man's credit and his courage"},{"time":677683,"text":"that he said, \"Yes, I will.\""},{"time":681299,"text":"A shocker in American jurisprudence."}]},{"cues":[{"time":685291,"text":"So in fact, we found the same identical conditions,"},{"time":687763,"text":"we reconstructed the entire thing again,"},{"time":689804,"text":"he came out with an entire brigade of sheriff's officers"},{"time":693814,"text":"to protect him in this community, all right? (Laughter)"},{"time":698971,"text":"We had him stand actually slightly in the street,"},{"time":704025,"text":"so closer to the suspect vehicle, the shooter vehicle,"},{"time":707205,"text":"than the actual teenagers were,"},{"time":709947,"text":"so he stood a few feet from the curb"},{"time":712171,"text":"toward the middle of the street."},{"time":714783,"text":"We had a car that came by,"},{"time":717700,"text":"same identical car as described by the teenagers, right?"},{"time":722651,"text":"It had a driver and a passenger,"},{"time":724588,"text":"and after the car had passed the judge by,"},{"time":728411,"text":"the passenger extended his hand,"},{"time":731925,"text":"pointed it back to the judge as the car continued on,"},{"time":736499,"text":"just as the teenagers had described it, right?"},{"time":738718,"text":"Now, he didn't use a real gun in his hand,"},{"time":741571,"text":"so he had a black object in his hand that was similar"},{"time":743989,"text":"to the gun that was described."},{"time":745968,"text":"He pointed by, and this is what the judge saw."}]},{"cues":[{"time":748814,"text":"This is the car 30 feet away from the judge."},{"time":755913,"text":"There's an arm sticking out of the passenger side"},{"time":758825,"text":"and pointed back at you."},{"time":761198,"text":"That's 30 feet away."},{"time":763163,"text":"Some of the teenagers said that in fact the car"},{"time":765355,"text":"was 15 feet away when it shot."},{"time":767931,"text":"Okay. There's 15 feet."}]},{"cues":[{"time":771595,"text":"At this point, I became a little concerned."},{"time":775765,"text":"This judge is someone you'd never want to play poker with."},{"time":780499,"text":"He was totally stoic. I couldn't see a twitch of his eyebrow."},{"time":784787,"text":"I couldn't see the slightest bend of his head."},{"time":788056,"text":"I had no sense of how he was reacting to this,"},{"time":791557,"text":"and after he looked at this reenactment,"},{"time":794597,"text":"he turned to me and he says,"},{"time":795677,"text":"\"Is there anything else you want me to look at?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":798935,"text":"I said, \"Your honor,\" and I don't know whether I was"},{"time":803430,"text":"emboldened by the scientific measurements that I had"},{"time":806387,"text":"in my pocket and my knowledge that they are accurate,"},{"time":810083,"text":"or whether it was just sheer stupidity,"},{"time":812338,"text":"which is what the defense lawyers thought — (Laughter) —"},{"time":815163,"text":"when they heard me say,"},{"time":816915,"text":"\"Yes, Your Honor, I want you stand right there"},{"time":819619,"text":"and I want the car to go around the block again"},{"time":823955,"text":"and I want it to come and I want it to stop"},{"time":827309,"text":"right in front of you, three to four feet away,"},{"time":831499,"text":"and I want the passenger to extend his hand"},{"time":834955,"text":"with a black object and point it right at you,"},{"time":836971,"text":"and you can look at it as long as you want.\""},{"time":842691,"text":"And that's what he saw. (Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":847118,"text":"You'll notice, which was also in my test report,"},{"time":850958,"text":"all the dominant lighting is coming from the north side,"},{"time":853603,"text":"which means that the shooter's face would"},{"time":855346,"text":"have been photo-occluded. It would have been backlit."},{"time":857962,"text":"Furthermore, the roof of the car"},{"time":859864,"text":"is causing what we call a shadow cloud inside the car"},{"time":864138,"text":"which is making it darker."},{"time":867468,"text":"And this is three to four feet away."}]},{"cues":[{"time":871580,"text":"Why did I take the risk?"},{"time":874708,"text":"I knew that the depth of field was 18 inches or less."},{"time":878937,"text":"Three to four feet, it might as well have been"},{"time":880604,"text":"a football field away."},{"time":885076,"text":"This is what he saw."},{"time":887284,"text":"He went back, there was a few more days of evidence"},{"time":891084,"text":"that was heard. At the end of it,"},{"time":893388,"text":"he made the judgment that he was going to grant"},{"time":896016,"text":"the petition for a retrial."},{"time":899094,"text":"And furthermore, he released Mr. Carrillo"},{"time":901572,"text":"so that he could aid in the preparation of his own defense"},{"time":904559,"text":"if the prosecution decided to retry him."}]},{"cues":[{"time":910578,"text":"Which they decided not to."},{"time":912888,"text":"He is now a freed man. (Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":917949,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":921892,"text":"This is him embracing his grandmother-in-law."},{"time":926996,"text":"He -- His girlfriend was pregnant when he went to trial,"},{"time":931071,"text":"right? And she had a little baby boy."},{"time":935156,"text":"He and his son are both attending Cal State, Long Beach"},{"time":937837,"text":"right now taking classes. (Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":944025,"text":"And what does this example --"},{"time":947988,"text":"what's important to keep in mind for ourselves?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":952332,"text":"First of all, there's a long history of antipathy"},{"time":956028,"text":"between science and the law"},{"time":958108,"text":"in American jurisprudence."},{"time":960508,"text":"I could regale you with horror stories of ignorance"},{"time":963956,"text":"over decades of experience as a forensic expert"},{"time":968292,"text":"of just trying to get science into the courtroom."},{"time":972798,"text":"The opposing council always fight it and oppose it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":977732,"text":"One suggestion is that all of us become much more"},{"time":981119,"text":"attuned to the necessity, through policy,"},{"time":983988,"text":"through procedures,"},{"time":986044,"text":"to get more science in the courtroom,"},{"time":989228,"text":"and I think one large step toward that"},{"time":991539,"text":"is more requirements,"},{"time":993381,"text":"with all due respect to the law schools,"},{"time":995940,"text":"of science, technology, engineering, mathematics"},{"time":1001051,"text":"for anyone going into the law,"},{"time":1003028,"text":"because they become the judges."},{"time":1006652,"text":"Think about how we select our judges in this country."},{"time":1009700,"text":"It's very different than most other cultures. All right?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1013060,"text":"The other one that I want to suggest,"},{"time":1015470,"text":"the caution that all of us have to have,"},{"time":1017900,"text":"I constantly have to remind myself,"},{"time":1019740,"text":"about just how accurate are the memories"},{"time":1022843,"text":"that we know are true, that we believe in?"},{"time":1028212,"text":"There is decades of research,"},{"time":1031596,"text":"examples and examples of cases like this,"},{"time":1035764,"text":"where individuals"},{"time":1037732,"text":"really, really believe. None of those teenagers"},{"time":1041244,"text":"who identified him"},{"time":1043076,"text":"thought that they were picking the wrong person."},{"time":1046352,"text":"None of them thought they couldn't see the person's face."},{"time":1049706,"text":"We all have to be very careful."},{"time":1051838,"text":"All our memories are reconstructed memories."},{"time":1055478,"text":"They are the product of what we originally experienced"},{"time":1057876,"text":"and everything that's happened afterwards."},{"time":1060609,"text":"They're dynamic."},{"time":1062660,"text":"They're malleable. They're volatile,"},{"time":1065148,"text":"and as a result, we all need to remember to be cautious,"},{"time":1069172,"text":"that the accuracy of our memories"},{"time":1072492,"text":"is not measured in how vivid they are"},{"time":1075996,"text":"nor how certain you are that they're correct."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1081127,"text":"Thank you. (Applause)"}]}]}